46
00:01:57,717 --> 00:01:59,385
dan deskripsi,

47
00:01:59,786 --> 00:02:00,753
yang membantu pengguna

48
00:02:00,820 --> 00:02:03,022
pahami apa fungsi widget ini.

49
00:02:03,857 --> 00:02:05,058
